{"data":[{"date":"09:25 15/06","title":"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal h\u1ecfi mua David Luiz</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u cho Chelsea. M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Conte khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a The Blues, sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua David Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua David Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/30/Arsenal-mua-David-Luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-nhung-bi-tu-choi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 David Luiz&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa Luiz v\u00e0 Conte v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p The Blues sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Luiz m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y Conte v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb v\u00e0 Luiz \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/monaco-muon-mua-david-luiz-172-185268.html\" target=\"_blank\">Monaco quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng c\u00f2n Chambers hay Holding kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Luiz s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. \u00d4ng Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Luiz, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/6/Chelsea-tu-choi-ban-David-Luiz-cho-Arsenal-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Luiz cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Theo Le10Sport, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, con s\u1ed1 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao David Luiz s\u1ebd&nbsp;ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"181","checkdouble":"188530"},{"date":"10:06 15/06","title":"Mario Gotze s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/8/25/Trung-ve-David-Luiz-va-nhung-vu-tro-lai-lich-su-hinh-anh-17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mario Gotze t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund, song s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Arsenal hay Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Arsenal hay Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/Mario-Gotze-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-Arsenal-hay-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d, Gotze ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Dortmund. Khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Gotze cho Dortmund l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gotze mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Gotze va ngay tro lai\" title=\"Mario Gotze v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/25/Trung-ve-David-Luiz-va-nhung-vu-tro-lai-lich-su-hinh-anh-17.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-dortmund-tha-thinh-liverpool-172-188137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gotze mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Klopp \u1edf Liverpool</span>. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Anfield l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Liverpool s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Mario Gotze. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf Premier League nh\u01b0 Everton, West Ham, Leicester v\u00e0 Newcastle \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gotze. Song ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"180","checkdouble":"188531"},{"date":"09:22 15/06","title":"HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-tite-tuc-gian-vi-dt-brazil-bi-lo-chien-thuat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, HLV Tite c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Gabriel Jesus.</h2><h2>\u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-tite-tuc-gian-vi-dt-brazil-bi-lo-chien-thuat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129&nbsp; t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, Brazil c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra Rostov chi\u1ec1u 14/6. \u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p trong 15 ph\u00fat kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Selecao v\u1eabn cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb &lsquo;ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y&rsquo; tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau khi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean trang Instagram.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u1ea1n phim \u0111\u00e3 quay c\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Neymar, Jesus, Willian, Coutinho, Paulinho v\u00e0 Marcelo theo m\u1ed9t \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch s\u1eb5n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Tite.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadp l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1eafng \u00c1o 3-0 cho th\u1ea5y HLV Tite \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho &lsquo;c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba&rsquo;. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m: Alisson, Danilo, Thiago Silva, Miranda, Marcelo, Casemiro, Paulinho, Coutinho, Willian, Neymar v\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil n\u0103m nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cao nh\u1ea5t, x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-so-do-co-the-giup-brazil-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-421-188416.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/3-so-do-co-the-giup-brazil-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-so-do-co-the-giup-brazil-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-421-188416.html\">3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Brazil th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Brazil d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Selecao th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho-421-188520.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho-421-188520.html\">5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd!</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u0103ng k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u01b0 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c hay Ph\u00e1p song h\u1ecd \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"179","checkdouble":"188532"},{"date":"09:57 15/06","title":"N\u00d3NG: M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/mu-gia-han-hop-dong-thanh-cong-voi-thu-thanh-dean-henderson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Man United v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U21 Anh Dean Henderson, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Dean Henderson l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><br>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/mu-gia-han-hop-dong-thanh-cong-voi-thu-thanh-dean-henderson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Dean Henderson t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 ba trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Dean Henderson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a M.U m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Shrewsbury theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i PFA League One c\u1ee7a n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020, k\u00e8m th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n k\u00e8m theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi k\u00eanh MUTV sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, Henderson vui v\u1ebb cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Shrewsbury theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng nay \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m sau m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba qua, tuy nhi\u00ean M.U v\u1eabn l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man-421-188523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man-421-188523.html\">Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 15/6: Sao MU s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (15/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"178","checkdouble":"188533"},{"date":"09:38 15/06","title":"Jesus xem nh\u1eb9 danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/jesus-xem-nhe-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00fap Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Jesus h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesus nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, Jesus s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Selecao l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Jesus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/6-ung-vien-sang-gia-cho-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup-2018-466-187535.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup</span> kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh khi Brazil b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus xem nh\u1eb9 danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jesus xem nh\u1eb9 danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/jesus-xem-nhe-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jesus xem nh\u1eb9 danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Tite c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Neymar, Coutinho v\u00e0 Willian ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n di chuy\u1ec3n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cV\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o hay m\u1ed9t pha t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng ngang nhau.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cS\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jesus khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e0n anh Firmino</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesus s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil thay v\u00ec Firmino, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Hoffenheim t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. V\u00e0 Jesus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Firmino l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Firmino. V\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3: S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a hai ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ee3i cho Brazil. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Th\u1eadt ra t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Firmino gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tite-tuc-gian-vi-dt-brazil-bi-lo-chien-thuat-421-188532.html\">HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-so-do-co-the-giup-brazil-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-421-188416.html\">3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Brazil th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"177","checkdouble":"188534"},{"date":"09:55 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-ai-cap-va-nhung-du-doan-khong-tuong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng logic h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 19h ng\u00e0y 15/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Ekaterinburg Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ekaterinburg)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Uruguay -0.94*0:1*0.88 Ai C\u1eadp<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.99*2 1/4*0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-ai-cap-va-nhung-du-doan-khong-tuong.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp 19h ng\u00e0y 15/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay, Bongda24h.vn c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111a s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki (Moskva). Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c, kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m World Cup th\u00ec ri\u00eang \u0110T Nga c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga thang Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Nga thang Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nga-thang-Saudi-Arabia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nga m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia 5-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u201c6 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u1edd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 Nga v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Saudi Arabia 5 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ai-cap-nhan-tin-vui-bat-ngo-tu-thanh-salah-421-188498.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ai C\u1eadp nh\u1eadn tin vui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb \u201cTh\u00e1nh Salah\u201d</span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh HLV Hector Cuper kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 100% r\u1eb1ng Salah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft Salah \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng qua cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 Uruguay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Ekaterinburg Arena 19h t\u1ed1i nay (15/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah\" title=\"Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay-19h-ngay-156-Salah-khong-quan-trong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ai C\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, gi\u1eefa c\u00f3 Salah v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng Salah l\u00e0 hai Ai C\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho CLB tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a 2017/18. Tr\u00ean \u0110TQG, ch\u00ednh anh c\u0169ng ghi t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n cho Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Congo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Uruguay c\u0169ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Salah. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Cavani c\u00f3 40 b\u00e0n th\u00ec Suarez c\u0169ng c\u00f3 31 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ph\u00eda sau \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 Rodrigo Bentancur, Matias Vecino, Cristian Rodriguez\u2026 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay tien dao Luis Suarez\" title=\"Uruguay tien dao Luis Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/181155-Uruguay-tien-dao-Luis-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay c\u00f3 Suarez \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Hector Cuper lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ai C\u1eadp ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. 12 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1eabn giao h\u1eefu, Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ai Cap HLV Hector Cuper\" title=\"Ai Cap HLV Hector Cuper\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Ai-Cap-tai-World-Cup-2018-Nin-tho-cho-Salah-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Cuper b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 B\u1ec9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh r\u1ed3i sau c\u00f9ng thua 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. N\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n (\u0111i\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf qua \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu), l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 45 tu\u1ed5i Essam El Hadary s\u1ebd c\u00f2n rung l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCavani v\u00e0 Suarez c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201ctr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean kh\u1eafc th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c song thi\u1ebfu tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2><strong>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: <br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Uruguay </strong>(s\u1ebd th\u1eafng) v\u00e0 <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Uruguay th\u1eafng 3-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ch\u1eb5n<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Ai C\u1eadp \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 qu\u1ea3 (-1 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Uruguay hi\u1ec7p 1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Ai C\u1eadp \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 qu\u1ea3 (-3/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 10 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (9 1/2).<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 5 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (4 1/2).<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng thua Uruguay (+1/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"176","checkdouble":"188535"},{"date":"10:17 15/06","title":"Sagna tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/3/sagna-tin-tuong-pogba-se-toa-sang-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sagna tin r\u1eb1ng Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sagna b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u00ean b\u1ed5ng xu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3m kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng Pogba nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Australia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Bacary Sagna kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sagna tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sagna tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/sagna-tin-tuong-pogba-se-toa-sang-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sagna tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin. Nh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi nghe nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n.<br />\r\n<br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u1ea1i sao Pogba b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch? V\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Pogba s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean ph\u00fa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1ea9m sinh nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br />\r\n<br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay xem c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10 ho\u1eb7c s\u1ed1 8. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6. V\u00e0 khi ch\u01a1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u00ean m\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Pogba b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em><br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Pogba ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sagna, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhin-vao-pogba-nguoi-ta-thay-van-de-cua-mu-172-161099.html\" target=\"_blank\">nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Pogba</span> c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. V\u00ec ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Pogba lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n t\u1eeb NHM. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i theo ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a HLV. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u1ede m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. C\u0110V kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p:<br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-diem-manh-va-3-diem-yeu-cua-dt-phap-o-world-cup-2018-421-188490.html\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/zidane-toa-sang-doi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-1998-thang-world-cup-all-star-98-421-188386.html\">Zidane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 th\u1eafng World Cup All Star 98</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"175","checkdouble":"188536"},{"date":"07:26 15/06","title":"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u0103ng k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u01b0 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c hay Ph\u00e1p song h\u1ecd \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6ChFe1-f_e4\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>1. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-thuy-si-tai-world-cup-2018-co-xung-voi-hang-6-the-gioi-421-188125.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Vladimir Petkovic, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y khoa h\u1ecdc. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 10 trong s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 thua, 1 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>2. Croatia</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u201cch\u00fa ng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng Ivan Rakitic, Luka Modric, Ivan Perisic hay Mario Mandzukic v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u0103ng k\u00ednh Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u0103ng k\u00ednh Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Video-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-lang-kinh-Bongda24hvn-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>3. Colombia</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brazil. N\u0103m nay, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 James Rodriguez hay Radamel Falcao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>4. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-uruguay-tai-world-cup-2018-duong-ta-thang-tien-421-187908.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay</span></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Uruguay d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0\u2026 \u0103n b\u00e1nh. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/5-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-Brazil,-Duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T\u00a0Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>5. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ngo\u00e0i Cris Ronaldo, hi\u1ec7n Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ea3n sinh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb trung s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"174","checkdouble":"188520"},{"date":"07:44 15/06","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 9: Nh\u1eadt k\u00fd ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-9-nhat-ky-world-cup-ngay-khai-mac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Bongda24h.vn nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u 14/6 c\u00f2n \u0111ang n\u00f3ng h\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 9:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IQP2TuA-Wbw\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf m\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. L\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c di\u1ec5n ra trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p to l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Vladimir Putin c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi khi Nga l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau l\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c r\u1ed9n r\u00e0ng, Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n Luzhniki (Moskva) v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0, \u201cG\u1ea5u Nga\u201d d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1 5 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 th\u00f4ng qua clip d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean truy c\u1eadp Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00e9!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZAiun8-d60VU6Px95pbGPA/videos\" target=\"_blank\">k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 5: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P2)</span><br>\r\n<span>S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 \u0111i qua 3 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/10/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P1)</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u, Bongda24h.vn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nhau b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec3m...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"173","checkdouble":"188521"},{"date":"07:53 15/06","title":"L\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/le-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-ruc-ro-sac-mau-cua-chu-nha-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. 3 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi tr\u00ean 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh c\u00f3 30 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane muon DT Anh len ngoi vo dich\" title=\"Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Kane-se-la-Vua-pha-luoi-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111i s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKieran Trippier, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Harry Kane, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u1ecdi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf c\u1ea3 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" title=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kieran Trippier cho r\u1eb1ng Kane quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Raheem Sterling hay Dele Alli ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh&nbsp;b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2014 t\u1ea1i Brazil, song Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t, Anh t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"172","checkdouble":"188522"},{"date":"07:53 15/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 15/6: 4 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u0110N th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn m\u1edf m\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (15/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha r\u1ed1i ren tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24h t\u1edbi, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngay trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. Trong khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o scandal thay t\u01b0\u1edbng 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi khai m\u1ea1c World Cup r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ramos \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00ec ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \"Seleccao\" t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1eeba l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \"th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p\". C\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 William Carvalho, Bruno Fernandes, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gelson Martins v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Rui Patricio v\u1eeba ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB Sporting v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Fernando Santos \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00eam nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/3_2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u00f4m m\u1ed9ng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Brazil. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 1h s\u00e1ng 18/6. Shaqiri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cMessi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\u201d cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe 100% s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ea5u Australia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Kylian Mbappe d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Australia ng\u00e0y 16/6 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai-421-188352.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai-421-188352.html\">Mbappe ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i</span><br>\r\n<span>Kylian Mbappe ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn NHM \u0110T Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Kane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kieran Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Trippier v\u00e0 Kane l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Tottenham. Theo Trippier, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Alli, Sterling hay Vardy c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"171","checkdouble":"188523"},{"date":"08:00 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay (19h ng\u00e0y 15/6): Salah c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-19h-ngay-156-salah-co-hay-khong-khong-quan-trong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng qua ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Cuper, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Salah v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay t\u1ed1i nay (15/6). Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, Mohamed Salah l\u1ea1c quan t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t ngay tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Salah g\u1ee3i cho C\u0110V \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1eafc Phi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may, Salah v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang ng\u00e0y 15/6 h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, tham gia c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ai-cap-nhan-tin-vui-bat-ngo-tu-thanh-salah-421-188498.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ai C\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn tin vui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh Salah&rdquo;</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay 19h ng\u00e0y 156 Salah kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay 19h ng\u00e0y 156 Salah kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay-19h-ngay-156-Salah-khong-quan-trong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Hector Cuper th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 100% s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c vui \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Mo Salah. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;C\u00e1c Pharaoh&rdquo;. C\u00f3 anh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Liverpool nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh \u1edf 2/3 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990 t\u1edbi nay. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Cuper r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Salah ra s\u00e2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 r\u1ee7i ro l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Ai Cap vs Uruguay\" title=\"Preview Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay c\u00f3 ch\u00fat thay \u0111\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Salah ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng. Anh v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i. Trong b\u1ea3ng A, Uruguay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/nga-huy-diet-saudi-arabia-salah-va-luis-suarez-buoc-phai-mot-mat-mot-con-466-188511.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nga, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Saudi Arabia 5-0</span> ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nga trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;6 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u1edf s\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9, h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Argentina, Colombia r\u1ed3i Chile&hellip; \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn khi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a La Celeste v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. N\u1ebfu Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Salah, Uruguay c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" title=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Uruguay-tai-World-Cup-2018-Duong-ta-thang-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 g\u00ec, Uruguay v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng Rodrigo Bentancur, Matias Vecino \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 r\u1ed3i Jose Maria Gimenez, Diego Godin \u1edf h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. \u1ede c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOscar Tabarez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Uruguay t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 World Cup n\u0103m 2010 v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng 1/8 n\u0103m 2014. \u00d4ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. V\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Uruguay ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp. Uruguay c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 Salah hay kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi v\u1eabn \u1edf &ldquo;chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi&rdquo; so v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Hadary &ndash; 7.Fathy, 6.Hegazi, 2.Gabr, 13.Shafy &ndash; 17.Elneny, 8.Hamed &ndash; 10.Salah, 19.Said, 21.Trezeguet &ndash; 9.Mohsen.<br>\r\n<strong>Uruguay (4-3-1-2):</strong> 1.Muslera &ndash; 16.Pereira, 2.Gimenez, 3.Godin, 22.Caceres &ndash; 6.Bentancur, 15.Vecino, 8.Nandez &ndash; 10.Arrascaeta &ndash; 9.Suarez, 21.Cavani.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Uruguay th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Maroc vs Iran\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Maroc-vs-Iran-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"170","checkdouble":"188524"},{"date":"08:38 15/06","title":"Kieran Trippier: \"Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh Harry Kane\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. 3 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi tr\u00ean 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh c\u00f3 30 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane muon DT Anh len ngoi vo dich\" title=\"Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Kane-se-la-Vua-pha-luoi-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111i s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKieran Trippier, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Harry Kane, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u1ecdi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf c\u1ea3 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" title=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kieran Trippier cho r\u1eb1ng Kane quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Raheem Sterling hay Dele Alli ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh&nbsp;b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2014 t\u1ea1i Brazil, song Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t, Anh t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"169","checkdouble":"188525"},{"date":"08:54 15/06","title":"Diego Godin: \"Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 Salah hay kh\u00f4ng c\u0169ng v\u1eady th\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Godin kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Salah c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Godin phat bieu ve Salah\" title=\"Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng A c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi Uruguay, b\u1edfi Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Diego Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Uruguay s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Salah, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Godin cho r\u1eb1ng Ramos v\u00f4 t\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Ramos ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m khi\u1ebfn Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Godin nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohamed Salah chan thuong sau pha va cham voi Sergio Ramos.\" title=\"Mohamed Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/salah-phat-bieu-ve-chan-thuong-o-chung-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin cho r\u1eb1ng Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1c \u00fd khi\u1ebfn Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Salah. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1c \u00fd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"168","checkdouble":"188526"},{"date":"08:12 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 4 v\u1eeba qua, Real Madrid c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Julen Lopetegui l\u00e0 HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 ng\u00e0y sau, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nguyen-nhan-thuc-su-dang-sau-viec-hlv-lopetegui-bi-tbn-sa-thai-421-188413.html\" target=\"_blank\">nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c HLV Lopetegui b\u1ecb TBN sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1edbi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 (RFEF) kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u cho hay h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Rubiales v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft tin Lopetegui \u0111\u1ebfn Real v\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 166 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 166 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-1h-ngay-166-Bo-tot-lac-loi-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Lopetegui r\u1eddi TBN m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh x\u1eed v\u00f4 ph\u00e9p t\u1eafc. H\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0110TQG n\u00e0o sa th\u1ea3i HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 20 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 t\u1edbi nay, Lopetegui \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (th\u1eafng 14, h\u00f2a 6). Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap La Roja h\u1ed3i sinh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Vicente Del Bosque, TBN \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN vs Thuy Si doi hinh\" title=\"TBN vs Thuy Si doi hinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-Dan-bo-tot-dang-bi-ton-thuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">La Roja \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ed3i v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 dung h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Sergio Ramos, Gerard Pique, Andres Iniesta hay David Silva&hellip; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1t khao th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG nh\u01b0 Dani Carvajal, Koke, Thiago Alcantara, Isco hay Marco Asensio&hellip; T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00f2a v\u00e0o l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha bay cao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia (v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018) hay 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap-421-188503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap-421-188503.html\">TBN \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n: Ramos &ldquo;t\u1ea9n&rdquo; nhau v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 scandal c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lopetegui - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Real</span>, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra 2 n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00f4i theo s\u00f4ng, theo bi\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; gi\u1edd \u0111ang l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi Fernando Hierro. Ch\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a RFEF \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u1edbi Hierro. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 do Lopetegui ch\u1ecdn ra v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10/23 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a TBN hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 theo \u00f4ng chinh chi\u1ebfn trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb U19 t\u1edbi U21 qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bo Dao Nha vs Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Preview B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1562018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec Lopetegui</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o l\u00fac \u0111ang kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3, m\u1ed9t T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi thay HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p ngay ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. So v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Seleccao c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Rui Patr\u00edcio, Pepe, Joao Moutinho, Ricardo Quaresma&hellip; song \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i tr\u1ebb trung, gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u1eefng m\u1ea1nh gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BDN ngoi sao Ronaldo\" title=\"BDN ngoi sao Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Algeria-(02h15-ngay-86)-Ha-guc-Bay-Cao-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u0110N&nbsp;c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng Andre Silva, Goncalo Guedes, Gelson Martins, Bernardo Silva&hellip; s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi CR7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 Lopetegui ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Qua \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song xem ra s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Olimpiyskiy (Sochi).<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nB\u0110N (4-4-2):</strong> 1.Patr\u00edcio - 21.C\u00e9dric, 3.Pepe, 6.Fonte, 5.Guerreiro - 11.Bernardo Silva, 14.Carvalho, 10.M\u00e1rio, 20.Quaresma - 7.Ronaldo, 9.Andre Silva<br>\r\n<strong>TBN (4-3-3): </strong>1.De Gea - 12.Odriozola, 3.Piqu\u00e9, 15.Ramos, 18.Alba - 10.Thiago, 5.Busquets, 6.Iniesta - 22.Isco, 19.Costa - 21.David Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 1-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bo Dao Nha vs Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/BDN-vs-TBN-(4-4-2-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"167","checkdouble":"188527"}]}